## Description ##
disable testcase test_gru_bidirectional temporarily, checked at https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/issues/11219.
@pengzhao-intel, @TaoLv

bad queryset pagination.


don't need this explicit return. Seems like it was a bandage that is no longer needed.

@mparent61 @MichaelButkovic

This allows us to deploy a nupic wheel and the wheels for the dependencies.

Fixes #2413

@scottpurdy @rhyolight

* Added `varargs` and `varkwds` iterators to `PKArgs` class;
* Implement getters/setters for core `Frame` class properties `.nrows`, `.ncols` and `.shape`;
* Python `Frame` class now inherits from core `Frame` class, allowing incremental transition for #1066;
* Removed from python `Frame` properties `.nrows`, `.ncols` and `.shape` since they are now inherited;
* Small improvements to `py::obj` class;
* The `Args` class now better integrates with `py::obj`;
* Added `py::otuple` class for easier tuple creation.

Uses #4028 as a base.

@jonparrott I assume that #4044 also applies to the database iterator, yes?
You did not explicitly say it did, and it is late so my brain is only partially working. Please advise.

change mVersion whenever NetworkData changes
change mStableVersion only when Stable NetworkData changes

